===more:Why did people admire Joe Louis and Babe Ruth? How did these athletes reflect contemporary American values? What athletes today do people consider admirable? What qualities do people admire in these athletes? Do you agree that these athletes are admirable? Why or why not? What if the athletes were named Mike Tyson or Randy Moss or Jason Williams or Ken Caminiti? Would you answer differently?

